  "identifier": "HJR 90",
  "title": "A JOINT RESOLUTION directing the establishment of the Real Estate Modernization Task Force.",
  "abstract": "Direct the Legislative Research Commission to establish the Real Estate Modernization Task Force to conduct a review of the real property laws of the Commonwealth; establish task force membership; require the task force to meet at least monthly during the 2026 Interim; require the task force to submit its findings and recommendations to the Legislative Research Commission by December 1, 2026.",
